***2)Pattern 2

--->>>

n=int(input("Enter a number: "))
for i in range(n):
    print(" "*(n-i-1),end="")
    print("*"*(2*i+1),end="")
    print(" "*(n-i-1))
    
    
    
***OUTPUT***


Enter a number: 4
   *   
  ***  
 ***** 
*******
> 
